<p><a style="font-size:18px; line-height:22px; height:22px;" href="/shiwenv_27a2fef94a30.aspx"><b>周颂·有客</b></a></p>
<p class="source"><a href="https://www.gushiwen.org/shiwen/default.aspx?cstr=%e5%85%88%e7%a7%a6">先秦</a><span>：</span><a href="/search.aspx?value=%e4%bd%9a%e5%90%8d">佚名</a></p>
<div class="contson" id="contson27a2fef94a30">
<p>有客有客，亦白其马。有萋有且，敦琢其旅。有客宿宿，有客信信。</p>
<p>言授之絷，以絷其马。薄言追之，左右绥之。既有淫威，降福孔夷。</p>
</div>
