<p><a style="font-size:18px; line-height:22px; height:22px;" href="/shiwenv_ce1086fcba9a.aspx"><b>隰桑</b></a></p>
<p class="source"><a href="https://www.gushiwen.org/shiwen/default.aspx?cstr=%e5%85%88%e7%a7%a6">先秦</a><span>：</span><a href="/search.aspx?value=%e4%bd%9a%e5%90%8d">佚名</a></p>
<div class="contson" id="contsonce1086fcba9a">
<p>隰桑有阿，其叶有难。既见君子，其乐如何。</p>
<p>隰桑有阿，其叶有沃。既见君子，云何不乐。</p>
<p>隰桑有阿，其叶有幽。既见君子，德音孔胶。</p>
<p>心乎爱矣，遐不谓矣？中心藏之，何日忘之！</p>
</div>
